name: Hamawta Runa
description:
in this work, for the first time, I found my generative art with a digital painting experiment

in the eternity of the infinite loop my mind burns relentlessly for crypto-art

inspired by Sacred Sounds and the Andean Icaros (similar to mantras) that help the spiritual awakening Hamawta Runa, initiate in Spirituality and Traditional Andean Medicine, based on the teachings of the Hamawta Thunupa Wiraqucha (11th century AD) towards spiritual awakening and path of self-knowledge from the Andean Cosmovision.

music by Angel BasSound Type crew connection
